@startuml
!theme plain
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "Wissenschaftler" as User
participant "Angular Frontend" as UI
control "Keycloak\n(Identity Broker)" as KC
boundary "AGOV\n(IdP)" as AGOV
participant "Core API (Backend)\n[Resource Server]" as Backend
database "PostgreSQL\n(Row-Level Security)" as DB

== Login & Token Issuance ==
User -> UI : Öffnet geschützten Bereich
UI -> KC : Redirect Login (Auth Code Flow + PKCE)
KC -> AGOV : Delegiert Authentifizierung
AGOV --> KC : Auth Success
KC -> KC : Mappt User-Rollen & Experiment-IDs\nin Token-Claims (realm_access.roles, experiment_ids)
KC --> UI : Return JWT (Roles, Experiment-IDs)

== API Request mit Row-Level Security ==
User -> UI : Klickt auf Experiment-Dashboard
UI -> Backend : GET /experiments/data\n(Header: Bearer JWT)
activate Backend

Backend -> Backend : Security Filter: JWT validieren\n(Signatur-Check via KC JWKS)
Backend -> Backend : MonteisJwtAuthenticationConverter: Rolle user -> api:read,\nRolle admin -> api:write + api:read-all,\nSub & Experiment-IDs -> MonteisPrincipal,\nals Authentication im SecurityContextHolder ablegen

Backend -> DB : set_config('app.read_all', ...)\nset_config('app.user_experiment_ids', ...)\n(RlsConnectionProvider, transaktionslokal)
Backend -> DB : jOOQ Query ausführen\n(unverändert, ohne manuelle\nBerechtigungs-WHERE-Klausel)
activate DB
DB -> DB : RLS-Policy wertet GUCs aus\nund filtert Zeilen serverseitig
DB --> Backend : Return gefilterte Datensätze
deactivate DB

Backend --> UI : 200 OK (autorisierte Daten)
deactivate Backend

UI --> User : Dashboard wird gerendert

@enduml
